{"tid":11274,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"懷疑d emoji撚係有組織黎搞事","createTime":"2016-11-29T08:45:28.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T09:38:29.000Z","uid":23829,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"59ed375e8642be0c035f5df29994a48ce9ad6296","tid":11274,"uid":23829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T08:45:28.000Z","msg":"最明顯係大部分支持用emoji既，佢地d回覆只會用emoji，唔會用高登icon<br />\n<br />\n另外佢講既野黎黎去去得幾句<br />\n1.呢度唔係高登，唔用emoji死番去高登<br />\n2.wtsapp都會用，點解呢度唔用得<br />\n3.唔俾人用emoji=保守<br />\n4.呢度俾用emoji，點解唔用得<br />\n<br />\n我只想回應第4點，高登都打到表情符號5p字，今日容忍到emoji，日後表撚情，5p字，殘體狗陸續有黎。 呢度既巴絲唔理你仲當自己係咪高登仔，唔該團結d。起碼我見d emoji撚既post都係負皮多，唔好俾佢地拋到。<br />\n搞串個場，又係咁叫人番高登，邊個最開心？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1fab8ca2cbc202cdbb0c89efa8be38a4bb50932","tid":11274,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T08:46:35.000Z","msg":"我覺得係搞事搵存在感多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d35c8f97a83479ff977f2f7b5e8b5ec1a0edcd46","tid":11274,"uid":23829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T08:48:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得係搞事搵存在感多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我越睇佢地講野個tone 越覺得背後係有組織<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"189f07dbde5d4647c1b0aab91152c805898cb2b4","tid":11274,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T08:49:13.000Z","msg":"👯"},{"pid":"1962b5abc6927fdfb46a95d0ea61c03f0b75cd05","tid":11274,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T08:51:36.000Z","msg":"唔止, 啲叫ADMIN秒回既POST都有啲咁既FEEL, 好似係特登玩嘢"},{"pid":"f2d0dd74a2d9726648c38ebf5486f9d0c25cede9","tid":11274,"uid":1644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29